# Debian-generic modular arm64 kernel baseline for kernel rk3588-mainline-7.1.
#
# GENERATED, not hand-curated -- do not hand-edit. This is the delta from the
# in-tree arm64 `defconfig` to the target RK1 kernel config, minus the
# rockchip soc/accel/device slices and minus toolchain-probed symbols (MTE, RELR,
# CC_*/AS_* -- each build host derives those). It carries the bulk Debian modular
# policy (filesystems, netfilter, media, USB, sound, ...) that is not rockchip
# engineering. Regenerated on a kernel bump; the small rockchip slices alongside
# it are the human-curated surface.

